{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "f6a7b8c9-d0e1-2345-f012-456789012345",
    "name": "Lav60 - Validar Cupom",
    "description": "Collection para **validar cupom** de um cliente em uma loja.\n\n## Fluxo recomendado\n\n1. Configure `base_url`, `x_token`, `tax_id_number`, `password`, `store_code` e `coupon_code`.\n2. Execute **Login com CPF** → salva `customer_id`.\n3. Execute **Validar Cupom**.\n\nOu use a pasta **Fluxo completo** no Collection Runner.\n\n## Importante\n\n- A validação **não aplica** o cupom — apenas confirma disponibilidade.\n- Após validar, use `coupon_code` no endpoint PIX.\n\nDocumentação: `docs/guides/validar-cupom.md`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "serverUrl",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:3100"
    },
    {
      "key": "x_token",
      "value": "SEU_X_TOKEN",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "tax_id_number",
      "value": "05791897405",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "password",
      "value": "sua_senha",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "coupon_code",
      "value": "ABC1234",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "customer_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "customer_jwt",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "storeCode",
      "value": "pb05"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Passo 1 — Login",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login com CPF",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json().data ?? {};",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_id', data.id);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_jwt', data.token);",
                  "    pm.test('customer_id salvo', () => pm.expect(data.id).to.not.be.empty);",
                  "    console.log('customer_id:', data.id);",
                  "    console.log('Próximo passo: Validar Cupom');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tax_id_number\": \"{{tax_id_number}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/customers/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "customers",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Obtém `customer_id` necessário para validar o cupom."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Passo 2 — Validar Cupom",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Validar Cupom",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('customer_id')) {",
                  "    console.warn('⚠ customer_id vazio — execute Login com CPF primeiro.');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json().data ?? {};",
                  "    const attrs = data.attributes ?? {};",
                  "    pm.test('Cupom válido', () => pm.expect(attrs.code).to.exist);",
                  "    console.log('\\n--- Cupom válido ---');",
                  "    console.log('Código    :', attrs.code);",
                  "    console.log('Tipo      :', attrs['coupon-type']);",
                  "    console.log('Aplicação :', attrs['apply-method']);",
                  "    console.log('Valor     : R$', attrs.value);",
                  "    console.log('Horário   :', attrs.start_time, '-', attrs.end_time);",
                  "    console.log('--------------------\\n');",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 400) {",
                  "    console.warn('400: cupom inválido para este cliente/loja');",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 404) {",
                  "    console.warn('404: cupom ou cliente não encontrado');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customer_id\": \"{{customer_id}}\",\n  \"store_code\": \"{{storeCode}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/coupons/{{coupon_code}}/validate",
              "host": [
                "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "coupons",
                "{{coupon_code}}",
                "validate"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Valida se o cupom pode ser usado pelo cliente na loja.\n\n**Não aplica o cupom** — use `coupon_code` no PIX após validar."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Fluxo completo",
      "description": "Run in order: Login → Validar Cupom",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Login com CPF",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json().data ?? {};",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_id', data.id);",
                  "    pm.test('Login OK', () => pm.expect(data.id).to.not.be.empty);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tax_id_number\": \"{{tax_id_number}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/customers/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "customers",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Validar Cupom",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const attrs = pm.response.json().data.attributes ?? {};",
                  "    console.log('Cupom OK:', attrs.code, 'R$', attrs.value);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customer_id\": \"{{customer_id}}\",\n  \"store_code\": \"{{storeCode}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/coupons/{{coupon_code}}/validate",
              "host": [
                "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "coupons",
                "{{coupon_code}}",
                "validate"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}